@startuml
!include ../shared/theme.puml

title Fluxify UML - Order Status State Machine

[*] --> PENDING

PENDING --> PROCESSING : Payment accepted
PENDING --> CANCELLED : Customer cancel or timeout

PROCESSING --> SHIPPED : Vendor dispatches package
PROCESSING --> CANCELLED : Refund approved

SHIPPED --> DELIVERED : Delivery confirmed

DELIVERED --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of PROCESSING
Inventory is already reserved during
order creation transaction.
end note

note right of DELIVERED
Review submission is enabled after
successful delivery.
end note

@enduml
